<li>Transcription of the Salmonella typhimurium spv virulence locus is regulated negatively by the nucleoid-associated protein H-NS .	[<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=8752327" target="_blank">8752327</a>, <a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=21398529" target="_blank">21398529</a>, <a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=21212121" target="_blank">21212121</a>, <a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=16428774" target="_blank">16428774</a>, <a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=15790293" target="_blank">15790293</a>]<br></li></div>
