<li>The transcriptional results in the absence of H-NS and LRP showed casA activity values of around 5,000 in MA medium ( Fig. 4 ) , while the expression value obtained in the presence of LeuO was only 500 ( Fig. 1C ) , indicating that LeuO moderately induces casA transcriptional expression and that some additional positive regulatory elements or signals are needed to obtain its complete induction .	[<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=21398529" target="_blank">21398529</a>]<br></li>
