<li>To determine whether the repressive effects of H-NS can be overcome by increased concentrations of K1-glutamate , different amounts of K1-glutamate were added to the reaction mixture to final concentrations of 0 , 100 , 200 , 300 , or 400 mM .	[<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=10766847" target="_blank">10766847</a>]<br></li>
