<li>It appears that a repressing structure is formed under these conditions , which is also promoted in the presence of H-NS FIG. 7 .	[<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=14594821" target="_blank">14594821</a>]<br></li>
