<li>Although H-NS reduces the transcription of more than 100 genes , it also is shown to be a negative regulator for rpoS translation ( 44,45 ) .	[<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=22256797" target="_blank">22256797</a>]<br></li>
