<li>The small nucleoid-bind-ing protein H-NS represses hilA in response to low osmolarity ( 84 ) .	[<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=19074398" target="_blank">19074398</a>]<br></li>
