<li>H-NS is considered a transcriptional repressor , playing a relevant role in silencing xenogeneic DNA ( 12 , 22 , 28 , 34 ) .	[<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=18039769" target="_blank">18039769</a>]<br></li>
