<li>We therefore investigated whether genes bound by H-NS displayed a particular topological or DNA sequence proﬁle around their putative regulatory regions .	[<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=16933988" target="_blank">16933988</a>]<br></li>
